description: With versatile vertical take-off and landing capability the VC-33 Mom`s Kitchen is the transport of choice for ferrying high ranking military personnel. The VC-33 is a small craft designed as a light passenger carrier featuring spacious interiors. It can travel at very high speeds comfortably and has a long operational range.A VC-33 transported http://anidb.net/ch7652 [Hayase Misa] and Captain http://anidb.net/ch10507 [Bruno Global] to the UN Forces Headquarters in Alaska, not long before Space War One came to a close.Source: http://www.macross2.net/m3/sdfmacross/momskitchen.htm
name: VC-33 Mom`s Kitchen
